name: Capital Group Multi-Sector Income Select ETFTM (Canada)
longDescription: Under normal circumstances, the Fund will invest at least 80% of its assets, taken at market value at the time of acquisition, in bonds and other debt instruments, which may be represented by other investment instruments, including derivatives.  Fund Seeks to provide a high level of current income.
